{"tid":95730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台北人北京開咖啡店 繁體字寫對了打9折","createTime":"2017-01-26T09:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-28T08:04:10.000Z","uid":48083,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe705a243781f22c1f883559cac25975bff591d","tid":95730,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:14:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpP5MtZP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpP5MtZP.jpg&h=6a30b50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/2017/new/jan/13/images/bigPic/400_400/phpsYe0hG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2F2017%2Fnew%2Fjan%2F13%2Fimages%2FbigPic%2F400_400%2FphpsYe0hG.jpg&h=34e32f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一名台灣人到中國北京經營「繁體字」咖啡館，學會繁體字正確筆劃的顧客還能享9折優惠。<br />\n《中央社》報導，中國北京這家名為「繁體字」的咖啡館，老闆娘李雪莉來自台灣，中文系畢業的她表示，自己在讀簡體字小說時很難被感動，因為簡體字無法呈現出一些文字背後的韻味。<br />\n<br />\n她舉例「髮」的筆劃多，有細髮如絲的感覺；而寫成簡體字「发」就失去這種味道。而例句「我的頭髮燒了」如果用簡體字表達，會分不清楚是「我的頭『發燒』了」還是「我的『頭髮』燒了」。出於對文字的喜愛，李雪莉開始在咖啡館裡教寫「繁體字」，介紹文字演變和部首意涵等內容。<br />\n報導指出，中國越來越流行繁體字，私章及店家招牌都可見到繁體字樣。到咖啡館學寫繁體字的學生，有人是為了查閱文獻方便，也有人單純是對繁體字很有興趣；李雪莉表示，在臨摹本上學寫繁體字、筆劃順序清楚的顧客可以打9折，現在許多顧客都說「來寫字」，而不是來喝咖啡了。"},{"pid":"3853d3c8a43a3a735f978ab2226a6f02f91c5c23","tid":95730,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"教識d 蝗蟲好難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fc470ed84f5827ffbe29c1afc2f79dd57da0ae","tid":95730,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教識d 蝗蟲好難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nＹＥＳ教精Ｄ蝗大檸樂"},{"pid":"295a825ebb8c47740f4f2bab403d4843fa5e344d","tid":95730,"uid":35914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教識d 蝗蟲好難分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔洗膽心喎,呢班人懶過晒"},{"pid":"efa709908e8b30927f7cf7a4a62c1d6234bae66c","tid":95730,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"分裂國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ed1dd6886483136c07782601606f2c0461be41","tid":95730,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d8d7faf5d279a5e20226dc36bbf161b2a35874","tid":95730,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:07:12.000Z","msg":"正體中文是人類歷史上最最最精美的智慧結晶<br />\n<br />\n形態美，象形到位<br />\n見字即懂意<br />\n字體多，系統完美<br />\n<br />\n傳意藝術並用<br />\n簡直是人類最偉大發明"},{"pid":"1d465def3f794ba3e6c5eca1947267b842d5f2af","tid":95730,"uid":27458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:10:19.000Z","msg":"On9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n消除兩岸差別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f24493b152f640a678b200e6f8e9dc4fe8c6329","tid":95730,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:18:17.000Z","msg":"大家都係蝗, 唔洗分得咁細 🤗"},{"pid":"a8f18547de0f4c7c33934fe1572e85f8204c4a0c","tid":95730,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:21:10.000Z","msg":"咪教班文盲啦"},{"pid":"260a22b74c562cf9b69a11a0a9d78b9505713d1c","tid":95730,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:22:36.000Z","msg":"要寫得出正確筆畫先得?<br />\n老實講句, 其實好多香港人寫字, 都未必會跟正確筆畫"},{"pid":"9424b3675e9b7e7e3510c1ae09e9a2c88fd87198","tid":95730,"uid":53060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T07:24: